{"lemma":"كَثْرَةُ","slug":"كَثْرَةُ","root":"ك.ث.ر","root_slug":"ك-ث-ر","root_link":"/words/roots/ك-ث-ر","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"كَثْرَة","root":"كثر","pos":"N","occurrence_count":2},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":2},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n36689","n36690","n36691"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%83%D9%8E%D8%AB%D9%92%D8%B1%D9%8E%D8%A9%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of كَثُرَ (kaṯura) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"plentiness, abundance, multitude"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/kaθ.ra/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n36689","headword_ar":"كَثْرَةٌ","root":"kvr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (S, A, K,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kivorapN","text_ar":"كِثْرَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) or the latter should not be used, for it is a bad dial. form, (S,) or it is correct when coupled with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qil~apN","text_ar":"قِلَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", for the sake of assimilation, (TA,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kuvorapN","text_ar":"كُثْرَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", though the first is the best known, (Ibn- 'Allán, in his Sharh el-Iktiráh,) or the last is not allowable, (TA,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kuvorN","text_ar":"كُثْرٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, A, K,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kivorN","text_ar":"كِثْرٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Muchness; much,"},{"kind":"text","text":"as a subst.;"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"copiousness; abundance; a large quantity; numerousness; multiplicity; multitudinousness; a multitude; a plurality; a large number; numbers;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"frequency: contr. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qil~apN","text_ar":"قِلَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, A, K.) [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kavura","text_ar":"كَثُرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":".] You say ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA lahu qul~N walaA kuvorN","text_ar":"مَا لَهُ قُلٌّ وَلَا كُثْرٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He has not little nor much"},{"kind":"text","text":"of property. (S.) And ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlHamodu lil~`hi EalaY Alqul~N waAlkuvori","text_ar":"الحَمْدُ لِلّٰهِ عَلَى القُلٌّ وَالكُثْرِ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, A,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EalaY Alqil~i waAlkivori","text_ar":"عَلَى القِلِّ وَالكِثْرِ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Praise be to God for little and much."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, * A.) [↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kuvorN","text_ar":"كُثْرٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"is explained in the S by"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kaviyrN","text_ar":"كَثِيرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and so in one place in the TA; but it is a subst., or an epithet in which the quality of a subst. predominates.] ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kavorapN","text_ar":"كَثْرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is also used to signify"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Richness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"wealthiness;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saEapN","text_ar":"سَعَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Mgh.)"}],"source_refs":["S","A","K","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n36690","headword_ar":"كُثْرَةٌ","root":"kvr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kavorapu","text_ar":"كَثْرَةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n36691","headword_ar":"كِثْرَةٌ","root":"kvr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kavorapu","text_ar":"كَثْرَةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":null}